<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4760312>
    dc:description "Figs. 9-14. Perlesta mihucorum, scanning electron photomicrographs. 9. Entire egg. 10. Collar pole. 11. Collar. 12. Details of collar and anchor fibers. 13. Micropylar pole. 14. Micropyles." ;
